Package tage.rml

Interface Angle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Angle>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Degreef, Radianf
    public interface Angle
extends java.lang.Comparable<Angle>
    An angle is the figure formed by two rays sharing the same vertex end point and represents a measurement of the amount of rotation between them.
    Author:
    Raymond L. Rivera
